<item>
            <title>[JCR-901] Support synonym searches</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-901</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>Jackrabbit should support synonym searches in the jcr:contains function like Google does.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Example:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
//element(*, nt:resource)[jcr:contains(., &amp;#39;~food&amp;#39;)]&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt; finds all nt:resource nodes that contain the word food or synonyms for food.</description>
